data.description: Come check out this rare find in the heart of Socorro! Close to shopping, freeway access and restaurants, this beautiful 4-bedroom home sits on a large/deep lot. Mature trees on front and backyard, storage in back and wood fence all around the front yard. Cute kitchen with great cabinets, appliances stay with the property. Ceiling fans, new water heater, spacious laundry room, the home is ready for a new owner! come see today!
